You're serious.

11:50.130 --> 11:54.254
♪♪

11:54.254 --> 11:56.256
I waved at a bunch
of white people today,

11:56.256 --> 11:58.008
and nobody
called the cops.

11:58.008 --> 12:00.801
Oh, my God.
 But the real victory --
I wore the same shoes

12:00.801 --> 12:04.144
I wore yesterday
and still got three compliments.

12:04.144 --> 12:06.847
I really love the way you
keep things in perspective, Dre.

12:06.847 --> 12:09.810
And one of our neighbors said
there's an HOA meeting tonight.

12:09.810 --> 12:11.651
So not miss out
on a moment,

12:11.651 --> 12:13.984
I think
I'm gonna go.
 Hmm.

12:13.984 --> 12:16.526
Uh, if you want some company,
I'm happy to go with you.

12:16.526 --> 12:18.618
Oh, that sounds like fun.
That's a good idea.

12:18.618 --> 12:21.822
He just wants to go pass out
his slam poetry fliers.

12:21.822 --> 12:24.865
I'll bring them along just in
case somebody wants to get woke.

12:26.166 --> 12:30.040
So, I went to the HOA, and I
 saw how much I'd been missing.

12:30.040 --> 12:32.632
In one night,
 I picked up some golf tips,

12:32.632 --> 12:36.216
learned a new handshake, and
 made an adorable new friend.

12:36.216 --> 12:39.589
So, I see you've met
Mr. Biscuits.

12:39.589 --> 12:40.680
What are you
doing here?

12:40.680 --> 12:42.803
I never miss
an HOA meeting.

12:42.803 --> 12:45.095
How do you think that tree
over our pool got cut down?

12:45.095 --> 12:46.266
Oh.

12:46.266 --> 12:48.268
Ah, Delores.

12:48.268 --> 12:51.892
We need to talk about
bringing in those trash bins.

12:51.892 --> 12:55.485
I got to admit, attending
 the HOA meeting made me feel

12:55.485 --> 12:58.398
how Columbus must have felt
 when he discovered America.

12:58.398 --> 12:59.609
Minus the genocide.

12:59.609 --> 13:01.781
Okay, okay, we're all --
we're all friends here.

13:01.781 --> 13:04.244
We can just be honest.

13:04.244 --> 13:05.996
So, you know, the Persian family
down the street.

13:05.996 --> 13:07.707
Well, they're putting
in columns,

13:07.707 --> 13:11.581
which I'm afraid
makes it look a little...

13:11.581 --> 13:12.913
too Persian.

13:12.913 --> 13:16.046
[ People murmuring ]

13:16.046 --> 13:17.838
You know
what I mean, Dre.

13:20.380 --> 13:24.224
Well, it doesn't exactly fit
into the neighborhood aesthetic.

13:24.224 --> 13:27.477
Yeah, right?
Told you guys he was cool.

13:27.477 --> 13:30.100
And even though the website
clearly says no guests,

13:30.100 --> 13:32.312
I'm so glad you brought
They Call Me Johan

13:32.312 --> 13:34.774
because I've -- I got
to hear his poetry.

13:34.774 --> 13:35.856
Here we go.

13:35.856 --> 13:39.239
I got a telescope
for my third eye.

13:39.239 --> 13:42.492
Guess you heard I...came
to Sherman Oaks

13:42.492 --> 13:44.784
to stay with
my sister's folks.

13:44.784 --> 13:47.077
I eat egg whites
with my toast.

13:47.077 --> 13:50.370
Too much cholesterol
in the yolks.

13:50.370 --> 13:51.952
They call me Johan.

13:51.952 --> 13:53.874
[ Laughs ]
 I don't.

13:53.874 --> 13:57.507
We should carpool to his
showcase and get French toast.

13:57.507 --> 13:58.798
Why?
 What was I
talking about --

13:58.798 --> 14:00.420
Oh-sidosies.
[ Laughs ]

14:00.420 --> 14:02.963
Well, looks like Janine's
"not problem"

14:02.963 --> 14:05.175
is rearing
its ugly head again.

14:05.175 --> 14:06.676
Whose turn is it
to drive her home?

14:06.676 --> 14:09.019
[ People murmuring ]

14:09.019 --> 14:13.233
♪♪

14:13.233 --> 14:15.395
You know what, guys?
I'll do it.

14:15.395 --> 14:16.937
Glad to lend
a helping hand.

14:16.937 --> 14:18.608
Why?
Because we live in a --

14:18.608 --> 14:19.859
Thanks, Dre.

14:19.859 --> 14:20.780
Oh. [ Chuckles ]

14:20.780 --> 14:22.282
Ow.

14:26.866 --> 14:28.828
Uh, what's for dinner?

14:28.828 --> 14:29.910
Give me a second,
guys.

14:29.910 --> 14:31.081
I'm --
I'm actually --

14:31.081 --> 14:33.293
I'm playing "Candy Crush,"
so...

14:38.338 --> 14:41.761
Should we
order something or...

14:41.761 --> 14:43.053
Uh...

14:46.927 --> 14:48.558
Mommy,
I'm starving.

14:53.513 --> 14:55.185
You know what, guys?

14:55.185 --> 14:57.857
I just realized I got to --
I got to go run some errands.

14:57.857 --> 14:59.519
I'm gonna...

14:59.519 --> 15:00.650
I'll be back.

15:00.650 --> 15:02.612
But...

15:02.612 --> 15:03.613
♪ Do do do ♪

15:03.613 --> 15:04.614
♪ Do do-do do do do ♪

15:04.614 --> 15:05.986
♪ Do do do ♪
 Junior, do the dab.

15:05.986 --> 15:07.077
Johan, do the dab.

15:07.077 --> 15:08.238
Janine, do the dab.

15:08.238 --> 15:09.329
This is corny.

15:09.329 --> 15:11.331
Siri, play N.W.A.

15:11.331 --> 15:13.663
♪ Straight outta Compton,
a brother with his finger... ♪

15:13.663 --> 15:15.125
Siri, please don't.

15:15.125 --> 15:17.127
All right, today
has been very chill

15:17.127 --> 15:19.339
and very unaggressive.

15:19.339 --> 15:21.001
Well, I hate to say
I told you so, but, uh...

15:21.001 --> 15:22.172
Oh, well,
you know what?

15:22.172 --> 15:24.594
I'm a man that can admit
when he's wrong.

15:24.594 --> 15:27.757
As soon as I put my
guard down and went to
my first HOA meeting,

15:27.757 --> 15:30.680
got to participate
in some casual racism...
 Ha.

15:30.680 --> 15:32.812
...and now I'm driving
a semiconscious

15:32.812 --> 15:34.054
white woman
home in her car.

15:34.054 --> 15:35.725
Life is good.

15:35.725 --> 15:37.057
[ Siren wails ]

15:37.057 --> 15:38.688
I blame myself.

15:43.273 --> 15:44.324
I can't believe
 I listened to Bow.

15:44.324 --> 15:45.525
BBD clearly said,

15:45.525 --> 15:47.197
"Never trust a big butt
 and a smile."

15:47.197 --> 15:48.618
Dad, nothing's
gonna happen.

15:48.618 --> 15:50.740
And if it does,
I have pre-paid legal.

15:50.740 --> 15:53.913
And I can't believe I listened
 to these two idiots.

15:53.913 --> 15:55.375
They got me to drop my guard

15:55.375 --> 15:57.417
and ignore 400 years
 of instincts.

15:57.417 --> 15:59.749
Anybody seen my wallet?
I need my I.D.

15:59.749 --> 16:01.381
For what? We're just going
up the street.

16:01.381 --> 16:03.713
Let's roll.

16:03.713 --> 16:05.925
And I wouldn't even have run
 into Janine this morning

16:05.925 --> 16:08.548
if I had taken my usual
 30 minutes

16:08.548 --> 16:11.721
to eloquently respond to racist
 YouTube comments.

16:11.721 --> 16:15.685
[ Keyboard keys clacking ]
 Dear K-K-Kevin...

16:15.685 --> 16:17.357
[bleep] you.

16:17.357 --> 16:18.598
What am I gonna do?

16:18.598 --> 16:20.560
People lose their licenses
all the time.

16:20.560 --> 16:22.652
Just tell the officer
you made an honest mistake.

16:22.652 --> 16:24.274
Mm.

16:24.274 --> 16:27.317
Funny story, I just started
wearing skinny jeans,

16:27.317 --> 16:29.489
and my wallet
doesn't fit in my pants.

16:29.489 --> 16:30.410
[ Cell door slams ]

16:31.701 --> 16:32.782
Damn it!

16:32.782 --> 16:35.075
Janine, where's
the registration?!

16:35.075 --> 16:36.876
Black lives
are at stake!

16:36.876 --> 16:39.999
Dad, can't you just tell
the officer whose car this is?

16:39.999 --> 16:42.212
I'm sure
they'll believe you.

16:42.212 --> 16:44.174
The registered owner
of the car

16:44.174 --> 16:45.755
is this passed-out
white woman.

16:45.755 --> 16:48.048
[ Cell doors slam ]

16:48.048 --> 16:49.389
Johan: Before you explain
anything,

16:49.389 --> 16:50.720
tell him you have
a video camera.

16:51.931 --> 16:53.012
Good evening, Officer.

16:53.012 --> 16:54.094
I just want to let you know

16:54.094 --> 16:55.345
that I'll be videotaping
tonight.

16:55.345 --> 16:56.686
[ Gunshot ]

16:56.686 --> 16:58.478
[ Rainbow crying ]

17:00.440 --> 17:01.811
You think it's too early
to holla at Bow?

17:01.811 --> 17:03.063
Mnh-mnh.

17:03.063 --> 17:05.315
Grief is treating her
so good.

17:05.315 --> 17:06.736
Line starts behind me.

17:06.736 --> 17:08.068
Hmm.
 Oh, God.

17:08.068 --> 17:09.199
I'll get in
that line.

17:09.199 --> 17:10.910
Hell, yeah.

17:10.910 --> 17:12.821
[ Sobbing ]

17:12.821 --> 17:14.493
Ooh.
 Mmm.

17:14.493 --> 17:17.867
You know what?
I'm tripping again.

17:17.867 --> 17:20.420
This is
Drake Summer '16.

17:20.420 --> 17:22.422
I'm just gonna go talk
to that officer

17:22.422 --> 17:24.334
and give him
a reasonable explanation.

17:24.334 --> 17:25.795
You know what?
I'm gonna tell him...

17:25.795 --> 17:27.087
♪ Straight outta Compton ♪

17:27.087 --> 17:28.548
♪ A brother with his finger
on the trigger ♪

17:28.548 --> 17:29.759
♪ But once I take out my... ♪

17:29.759 --> 17:31.471
[ Siren wailing ]

17:31.471 --> 17:32.472
Hey.

17:32.472 --> 17:33.513
[ Clears throat ]

17:33.513 --> 17:36.136
So, your pimp moves
are working.

17:36.136 --> 17:37.307
[ Chuckles ]

17:37.307 --> 17:38.978
Do you think I could feed
the kids now?

17:38.978 --> 17:39.849
I ate their supper.

17:39.849 --> 17:41.771
What?

17:41.771 --> 17:45.525
Oh. I get it.

17:45.525 --> 17:48.148
You think if they're hungry,
they'll appreciate me more.

17:48.148 --> 17:49.819
Now focus.
 Oh, okay.

17:49.819 --> 17:51.651
You got to make 'em
jealous now, Bow.

17:51.651 --> 17:53.323
Then you'll have them eating
right out the palm of your hand.

17:53.323 --> 17:55.325
Okay.
 But just
figuratively

17:55.325 --> 17:56.366
'cause I ate
their supper.

17:56.366 --> 17:57.657
Yes.

17:57.657 --> 17:58.868
All of their supper.

17:58.868 --> 17:59.829
[ Kids laughing ]
 Here they come.

17:59.829 --> 18:01.701
Oh, shoot.

18:01.701 --> 18:02.752
Turn off your heart.

18:02.752 --> 18:05.044
Just shut it down.

18:06.706 --> 18:08.087
Oh, hey, you guys.

18:08.087 --> 18:09.919
Gosh, I didn't even
hear you come in.

18:09.919 --> 18:12.712
So busy looking at pictures
of your cousins that --

18:12.712 --> 18:15.885
Oh, man,
they've gotten so tall.

18:15.885 --> 18:17.387
Oh, wow.

18:17.387 --> 18:20.600
They make such insightful
comments on Facebook.

18:20.600 --> 18:21.981
[ Laughs ]
 I'll be
the judge of that.

18:23.433 --> 18:25.355
Wow.

18:25.355 --> 18:27.777
Diamond really is wise
beyond her years.

18:27.777 --> 18:30.940
I see cousin Cha-cha's dating
an Abercrombie model.

18:30.940 --> 18:32.782
Yeah.
 Good for her.

18:32.782 --> 18:34.154
Don't look at pictures
of them.

18:34.154 --> 18:36.446
Look at my real face.

18:36.446 --> 18:38.077
Look.
Look.

18:38.077 --> 18:39.829
Oh.

18:39.829 --> 18:42.081
[ Chuckles ]
Oh.

18:46.416 --> 18:47.917
Wow.

18:47.917 --> 18:49.249
Check out
cousin Dante.

18:49.249 --> 18:50.380
Dre?
 Hm?

18:50.380 --> 18:52.342
What are you
doing here?
 What?

18:52.342 --> 18:54.133
I've been here
in this outfit

18:54.133 --> 18:55.385
looking at
Facebook pictures

18:55.385 --> 18:57.427
all night long
with you, right?

18:57.427 --> 18:59.219
I mean, that's the story
we'll tell the cops if they ask.

18:59.219 --> 19:02.101
The what?
 Don't worry about it.

19:03.102 --> 19:04.564
[ Sighs ]
 You're alive.

19:04.564 --> 19:07.357
I-I-I-I know
I sounded surprised,

19:07.357 --> 19:10.149
but I knew he was alive
because I am a very good parent.

19:10.149 --> 19:11.901
How did you get here?

19:11.901 --> 19:13.863
I did what you did.
I ran.

19:13.863 --> 19:14.944
And they
didn't catch you?

19:14.944 --> 19:17.537
Nope. Turns out it's true
what they say.

19:17.537 --> 19:19.579
You don't have
to outrun the cops.

19:19.579 --> 19:21.040
You only have to outrun
your uncle.

19:21.040 --> 19:22.872
[ Laughs ]
That's my boy!

19:22.872 --> 19:24.784
I have never been
more proud of you, son.

19:24.784 --> 19:26.246
Hold up, you guys.
 What?

19:26.246 --> 19:27.457
What is all this talk
of cops?

19:27.457 --> 19:28.498
And where's my brother?

19:28.498 --> 19:29.879
[ Door opens ]
 Dre: I don't know.

19:29.879 --> 19:31.170
Oh, my --
Oh, my God!

19:31.170 --> 19:33.132
Johan, are you okay?

19:33.132 --> 19:35.004
I may never be
okay again.

19:35.004 --> 19:36.506
After your husband
took off,

19:36.506 --> 19:38.388
things went about as badly
as they could go.

19:38.388 --> 19:40.970
Snitch.
 Dre, did you leave
my brother?

19:40.970 --> 19:44.974
Oh, so it's my fault that his
white instincts to investigate

19:44.974 --> 19:47.517
is stronger than
his black instincts to run.

19:47.517 --> 19:49.188
I ran.

19:49.188 --> 19:50.610
Shouldn't have gone back
for the fliers,

19:50.610 --> 19:53.573
but I learned
some very important lessons.

19:53.573 --> 19:55.815
Like pre-paid legal
is not a real thing.

19:55.815 --> 19:57.987
And also,
you should not attempt

19:57.987 --> 20:00.370
a citizen's arrest
on a police officer.

20:00.370 --> 20:03.823
I've also learned
that we are very, very far away

20:03.823 --> 20:06.085
from things
being completely different.

20:08.207 --> 20:11.671
I think what Uncle Johan
is trying to say is...

20:11.671 --> 20:14.964
it's still a crime
to be black...

20:14.964 --> 20:16.215
Rainbow: Oh.

20:16.215 --> 20:19.339
...if you're Kevin Hart
or Shaq.

20:19.339 --> 20:24.103
So mind your P's
and your Q's

20:24.103 --> 20:27.687
unless you want
to be abused.

20:30.109 --> 20:32.612
They call me --
 Shut up.

20:32.612 --> 20:34.354
Shut up.

20:34.354 --> 20:35.445
Is that how I sound?

20:35.445 --> 20:36.906
Worse.

20:36.906 --> 20:38.067
You're a grown man.

20:39.529 --> 20:41.070
Now, come on.

20:41.070 --> 20:42.452
Let's go see
what they did to Janine.

20:42.452 --> 20:43.953
I think you were wonderful,
Junior.

20:43.953 --> 20:46.125
Thanks, Mom.
 You sound
like your uncle.
 Let's go.

20:46.125 --> 20:47.707
Don't encourage it.

20:52.372 --> 20:53.543
You know what truly makes
 America great?

20:53.543 --> 20:54.794
All of our different
 communities,

20:54.794 --> 20:58.428
each one committed
 to helping all of its members.

20:58.428 --> 21:01.180
But then we're all
 still willing to change

21:01.180 --> 21:02.842
so we never miss a moment.

21:02.842 --> 21:04.554
Wait a minute.
 Hmm?

21:04.554 --> 21:07.016
So, the black driver's now
friends with the old white lady?

21:07.016 --> 21:08.308
That's some
bull[bleep]

21:08.308 --> 21:10.099
I told you.
 Fine, all right.

21:10.099 --> 21:12.522
Go ahead. Fast-forward to the
end of the movie "The Help."

21:12.522 --> 21:14.314
Okay, I'm telling you
right now

21:14.314 --> 21:16.566
if the poo pie works out,
I'm gonna lose my mind.

21:16.566 --> 21:18.197
Okay.

21:18.197 --> 21:21.661
And that's what truly makes
 America great.

21:21.661 --> 21:22.822
What?!
